&lt;p&gt;This role serves as a regional thought partner transforming complex data into actionable insights that inform decision‑making across sales, marketing, market access, and early commercialization activities. The AD operates closely with cross‑functional stakeholders to ensure analytics efforts are aligned to regional priorities, launch needs, and evolving market dynamics across Europe.&lt;/p&gt;
