&lt;p&gt;Business Analytics &amp;amp; Insight Generation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the application of statistical methods, modeling, and analytical techniques to support regional Oncology commercial and medical initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver actionable insights that inform prioritization, investment decisions, and execution across Europe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify emerging trends, risks, and opportunities through rigorous quantitative and qualitative analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Commercial &amp;amp; Early Commercialization Support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide analytics and insight support to regional commercial planning, brand strategy, and go‑to‑market activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with global and regional teams on early commercialization and scenario planning efforts relevant to Europe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support opportunity assessments, forecasts, and market sizing to inform strategic decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Market Landscape &amp;amp; Competitive Insights&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate the European market landscape, including competitive dynamics, access environments, and evolving healthcare trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor changes in market structure, customer behavior, and policy that may impact Oncology strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex market intelligence into clear, actionable implications for non‑technical stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Enablement &amp;amp; Insight Delivery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce and curate data sets required to generate insights across Commercial and Medical stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with internal teams to ensure data integrity, consistency, and relevance for regional needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present insights in clear, compelling narratives tailored to senior regional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
