&lt;li&gt;Leads the development and execution of branded and unbranded tactical plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimizes tactical plans based on qualitative and quantitative data and end-user utility (i.e. field feedback and call logging)&lt;/li&gt;
