&lt;li&gt;Possess expert project manager and process manager skills, specifically for Commercial Review Team (CRT) and with agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearly understands HCP Promotional Team goals, brand strategic imperatives, key objectives and competitive landscape, and contributes to the development of strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
