&lt;li&gt;Endocrinology, metabolic disease, or related specialty therapeutic area experience a bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience leading cross-functional initiatives and influencing senior stakeholders without direct authority&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Up to 25% domestic travel (location-based) or 30–35% (fully remote)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open to all locations. Role can be location-based (in office up to 3 days per week) or fully remote, with expected travel to office and meetings as needed&lt;/li&gt;
